Version: 1.0.3

Description:
This app visualizes compliance, network sessions and authentication data of your macmon NAC system in a very pretty and convenient way.

Supported versions:
macmon, version 6.0.0 or later with the Premium Bundle license
Splunk Enterprise, version 9.2 or later

Configuration and Troubleshooting:
Please refer to the white paper on https://portal.macmon.eu or contact support@macmon.eu  directly.